    x1 = Temperature
    y = Stress

    Parameters:
        params[0]: linear strain coefficient (modulus base)
        params[1]: quadratic strain coefficient
        params[2]: cubic strain coefficient
        params[3]: temperature decay rate of stiffness (exponential softening)
        params[4]: interaction term coefficient (strain*temperature)
        params[5]: linear temperature offset term
