      params[4]: quadratic strain coefficient
      params[5]: quadratic temperature coefficient
      params[6]: cubic strain coefficient
      params[7]: cubic temperature coefficient
      params[8]: quadratic strain * temperature interaction coefficient (x0^2 * x1)
      params[9]: strain * quadratic temperature interaction coefficient (x0 * x1^2)
      params[10]: quartic strain coefficient (x0^4)
      params[11]: quartic temperature coefficient (x1^4)

    Returns:
