        + p6*np.exp(p7 * x1) * x0  
        + p8 / temp_kelvin * x0  
        + p9*np.tanh(p10 * x0)
        + p11*np.log(strain_safe + offset)
        + extra_terms_combined

    We combine cubic and inverse squared temp terms into existing params by scaling or approximating.

