      4: tanh amplitude (strain saturation amplitude)
      5: tanh argument scale (strain saturation scale)
      6: cubic tanh coefficient (nonlinear strain)
      7: exp decay multiplier for thermal softening on strain
      8: exp decay rate w.r.t. temp inside exp()
      9: logarithmic strain hardening coefficient
     10: quadratic strain-temperature interaction coefficient in nonlinear term
     11: inverse temperature stiffening scale

    """
    
    epsilon = 1e-6
    
    # Unpack parameters for clarity
    bias = params[0]
    a_strain = params[1]
    a_temp = params[2]
    a_strain_temp = params[3]
    
    tanh_amplitude = params[4]       # amplitude of tanh saturation effect on strain
    tanh_scale = params[5]           # scale of tanh argument
    
    cubic_tanh_coeff = params[6]     # cubic power coeff on saturated strain
    
