      params[8]  : exponential decay rate w.r.t. temperature and strain squared
      params[9]  : log term coefficient (strain)
      params[10] : interaction multiplier (tanh^3 * sqrt(temp))
      params[11] : inverse temperature multiplier (stiffening/softening)

    """
    
